
1. terminal: eas login
// first time
2. terminal: npx eas build:configure
3. terminal: npx eas build --platform android --profile development
--------------------------
4. device: scan the QR code on the expo build
5. device: download and install distribution build
6. device: start the app
6. terminal: npx expo start --dev-client
7. device: scan the QR code on the terminal
8. copy the url from qr code scanner
9. paste the url to the app and connect
10. terminal: npx react-native log-android  // for console


npx expo start --dev-client
npx react-native log-android
